" event for :ref:`InputEventKey <class_InputEventKey>` events, unless "
"``allow_echo`` is ``true``). Not relevant for events of type "
":ref:`InputEventMouseMotion <class_InputEventMouseMotion>` or "
":ref:`InputEventScreenDrag <class_InputEventScreenDrag>`."
