"(:ref:`InputEventKey <class_InputEventKey>`), button "
"(:ref:`InputEventJoypadButton <class_InputEventJoypadButton>`) or action "
"(:ref:`InputEventAction <class_InputEventAction>`)."
msgstr ""
"如果给定的输入事件正在检查相同的键（:ref:`InputEventKey "
"<class_InputEventKey>`）、按钮（:ref:`InputEventJoypadButton "
"<class_InputEventJoypadButton>`）或操作（:ref:`InputEventAction "
"<class_InputEventAction>`），则返回 ``true``。"

